<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>LogicForge - Password Reset</title>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      color: #333333;
    }

    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .email-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5f0a87, #a4508b);
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .email-header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 26px;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 24px 20px;
    }

    .email-body p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .otp-code {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #5f0a87;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    a {
      color: #5f0a87;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 620px) {
      .email-body, .email-header, .email-footer {
        padding: 16px;
      }
      .otp-code {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>
        We received a request to reset the password for your LogicForge account.
        Please use the following OTP to reset your password:
      </p>
      <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
      <p>
        This OTP is valid for 5 minutes. If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.
      </p>
      <p>If you need further assistance, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>
        For any questions, contact us at
        <a href="mailto:l.f.logicforge@gmail.com">l.f.logicforge@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>